# Edge serverless functions (Vercel) — server-side values. Never commit real secrets.
#
# POST /v1/waitlist (api/waitlist.ts) persists to the shared waitlist_entries
# table. Set DATABASE_URL on the Vercel project (Production + Preview) to the
# same Postgres the migrations were applied to. Vercel Postgres also exposes
# POSTGRES_URL, which the function reads as a fallback.
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://vygo:vygo@localhost:5432/vygo
# POSTGRES_URL=

# Optional: extra allowed browser origins (comma-separated) beyond the default
# https://www.vygo.ai and https://vygo.ai. Requests with no Origin header
# (server-to-server) are always allowed.
# ALLOWED_ORIGINS=https://staging.vygo.ai
